;;; Commentary:
;;
;; This is a simple org-mode add on that allows the use of org mode as
;; an email database.
;;
;; Store emails in org structure like this:
;;
;; * Nic Ferrier
;; ** email
;; *** nferrier@gnu.org

;;; Source code
